      "text": "- Modal is focused: user fills fields without page layout shifting\n- Only \"Name\" is required; all others optional\n- On submit: modal closes, new KB auto-selected in dropdown\n- Page shows empty state with Upload + Import URL buttons ready\n- User immediately starts adding documents to the new KB\n- Fields: Name*, Industry, Entity Type, Company, Source URL\n- Cancel or click outside = modal closes, nothing created",
